      {
        "heading": "Clinical Note",
        "section_value": "Acute right ankle sprain.\nPLAN\nWe reviewed the patient's x-rays in detail today. The plan is to place the patient in an Aircast and provide the patient with crutches. I have also prescribed the patient meloxicam 15 mg to treat the pain. I have advised her to ice the area for 20 minutes 5 times per day. She can weight-bear as tolerated. I anticipate that she will improve in the next 2 weeks. If her pain does not improve with the Aircast, I will recommend formal physical therapy or pursuing further imaging.",
